<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>Lal Immanuel!</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1. Lungkham buoina dogal a lien ie,
 Lungngaih ni hin aw Na eng hung vak dawk hen;
 Gal a lien ie Setan gal a lien ie,
 Ei veng inla Na gam pello di'n.

[V2]
 Ei taihsan kin, ka Lal Immanuel,
 Ka hun ngai pen ie khawvel ahin;
 Buoina gal chu hung lien mahleh,
 Ka bitna galvenbuk, kulhpi Na hi.

[V3]
 2. Aw Hukdampa thepna gal lien chun,
 &quot;Hun pieng ka ting aw, Gehen gam nuom&quot; a tii;
 Ka chieh ngam puoi mi gilo gawtmun chu,
 Na gam gal muong Kanaan gam lo chu.

[V4]
 3. Nawpna pielgal ah leng mahleh chin,
 Hun sam zel ingka Hukdampa mel deihum;
 A hung lien ie Na gam do gitloh gal,
 Kei din chiehna a khak, Nang zo in.

[V5]
 4. Na vak zam vel lalna gamnuom ah,
 Gal a um ta puoi maw lungkham ta puong ka;
 Muh ka nuom ie kei le ei pui kai in,
 Angel vam leh mithienghaw lenna.</lyrics>
<hymn_number>121</hymn_number>
</song>